Trend Line of height_cm

data %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=survey_date, y=height_cm, group=pop, color=pop)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method="lm")
## `geom_smooth()` using formula = 'y ~ x'

Box Plot

data %>%
  filter(survey_date == "2023-01-27") %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=pop, y=height_cm, group=pop)) +
  geom_boxplot()
